---
// Arabic Poem Banner Component
// A decorative banner displaying an Arabic poem verse
---

<div class="group mx-auto block max-w-3xl px-4 pt-8" dir="rtl" lang="ar">
  <p
    class="text-right text-base leading-relaxed text-heading/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-heading sm:text-center md:text-lg lg:text-xl"
  >
    <span class="block sm:inline"
      >وَلْتَعْلَمِي أَنَّهُ لا بَأْسَ لَوْ عَثَرَتْ</span
    >
    <span class="hidden w-2 sm:inline-block md:w-4 lg:w-6"></span>
    <span class="block pr-12 sm:inline sm:pr-0"
      >خُطَى الأكارمِ حَتَّى يَعرِفُوا السَّدَدَا</span
    >
  </p>
</div>
